INSTALLATION
============

Requirements:
  bash gawk

Recommended:
  rdiff-backup duplicity rsync borg gzip hwinfo sfdisk cryptsetup flashrom hwinfo

Installation:
  To install backupninja, simply do the following:

  $ ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ make install

  You may wish to change the install locations, or other options. To find
  the available possibilities, run ./configure --help.

